    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "\"No wings but vertical and horisontal fins on rear 1/3",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "text": "of the rocket.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "\"No visable means of propulsion such as propeller,",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "vapor trail, smoke or exhaust.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "text": "\"The front of the rocket was very sharp with a needle",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "nose, the needle looked about 6\" long and was the size of a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "lead pencil.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "text": "\"The rear end was blunt similar to the rear end of a",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "jet fuselage.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "\"I was flying my ship ... and was traveling about 100",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "m.p.h. at the time.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "\"I was at 3450 ft. above sea level at the time.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "\"I was flying a compass course of 60 degrees, and the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "rocket was traveling almost west at 240 degrees.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "\"It happened about 2:45 P.M. on the above date.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "\"The visability was exceptionally good, about 30 miles.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "\"The yellow object looked very sharp and clearly outlined",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "because of the dark green background.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "\"If you will refer to the Huntington sectional aerial",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "map this object was sighted over a very small town named",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "Lubeck, which is about 4 miles direct west of South Parkersburg.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "\"It appeared to have spent it's force and seemed to be",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "dropping slightly as it passed by, or had been fired or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "launched from a higher altitude than the altitude I was flying.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "The above has been furnished to you for your information and",
      "status": "image_matched"
